.row.title-search{:style => "background: url('assets/city-img-1.jpeg') no-repeat;", :class => ("title-search-hompage" unless !current_page?(root_path))}
  .col-md-8
    .row
      .col-md-12.header-title
        %h2
          SpaceLender
          %br
          %small
            Find space for the things you need to do.
      .col-md-12
        = form_tag(users_search_path) do
          = text_field_tag :search, nil, :class => "form-control", :placeholder => "Search for spaces."
.container
  .row.text-center
    .col-md-4
      %h3
        List
      %p
        Take some pictures, state a renting price, and list your space. Then, wait for an interested person to contact you.
    .col-md-4
      %h3
        Lend
      %p
        Lend your listed space and send your clients an invoice for the space borrowed. You can even require a deposit!
    .col-md-4
      %h3
        Earn
      %p
        <strong>GET PAID!</strong> You just turned the free space that was always <em>just sitting there</em> into a money-maker! Even after it's been used, you can keep the listing up and allow more people to use it in the future.